        Changelog
        ---------
        
        0.2.0 (10/27/2013)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * Compatibility with TextBlob>=0.8.0.
        
        0.1.0 (09/25/2013)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * First release
        * Basically a thin, Py3-compatible wrapper around pattern.fr. Hooks to pattern's tagger and sentiment analyzer.
        
        
        0.0.1 (09/22/2013)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * Experimental release.
        
